z=\max(x+b,y)
P(z) = \int_{-\infty}^{\infty} dx \int_{x+b}^\infty dy\; P_1(x) P_2(y) \delta(z-y) + \int_{y-b}^\infty dx \int_{-\infty}^\infty dy\; P_1(x) P_2(y) \delta(z-x-b)
= P_2(z) \int_{-\infty}^{z-b} P_1(x)\;dx + P_1(z-b)  \int_{-\infty}^z  P_2(y)\;dy
